{"word":"βαθύνω","slug":"βαθύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βαθύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαθύς'><el>βαθύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to deepen, hollow out</i>, of a torrent, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <i>to dig deep</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as military term, <i>to deepen</i>, <el>τὴν φάλαγγα</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}